data.description: $5,000 PRICE REDUCTION!!! This move-in-ready 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is located in the popular subdivision of Santa Rita Ranch, centrally located to freeways, shopping, entertainment, hospitals, the airport, and top-notch schools—including LEGACY TRADITIONAL SCHOOL just steps away. Situated on a cul-de-sac lot, this home boasts an inviting curb appeal that sets the stage for the exceptional features within. As you step inside, you're greeted by a bright and charming interior highlighted by vaulted ceilings, wood-look plank floors, a neutral palette, and an abundance of natural light, open & bright eat-in kitchen, fully equipped with stainless steel appliances, track lighting, a pantry, cabinets adorned with crown molding, and a convenient breakfast bar & granite countertops. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or enjoy casual meals with family, this kitchen is designed to meet your needs. The master bedroom is split from the other 2 bedrooms & is a sanctuary of comfort with a custom shiplap wall, offering a lavish ensuite with soaking tub, dual sinks and a LARGE spacious walk-in closet, laundry room is directly off the master bedroom & each of the three bedrooms features carpet where the rest of the home has tile or wood laminate plank flooring. Step outside to a spacious backyard featuring a lush grassy area, a covered & extended paver patio, and a charming firepit. It's the perfect setting for entertaining guests, enjoying family gatherings, or simply unwinding after a busy day.
